        <abstract>
            <p>Congratulations on marriage, which CD considers the best and only chance for happiness in this world.</p>
            <p>Glad HWB is near completion of book.</p> 
<p>Begs him to thank Wallace for <hi rend="italic">Melastoma</hi> information; CD "cannot endure being beaten by a beggarly flower".</p> 
        </abstract>
